{
  "stem": "1029.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were not aware where the food was coming from.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure we paid for it because people still had money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they let us keep our money and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't take anybody's fillings or any teeth or any stories like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They, they said that they are not going to take our houses or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In other words, they are not going to-- they're going to keep our houses for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we knew better.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, my mother beforehand-- I mean, I didn't know about this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my mother has, has dug some holes and put some silverware in, you know, that-- you know, some of the family heirlooms and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she did-- some of the more important items, she took down into the well, loosened a couple of bricks, and put the-- put the jewelry or trinkets behind the brick.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She put that away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I don't remember it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I heard about it after we came back from the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Totkomlos, it was a nice place, I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had-- we had the equivalent of 7-Eleven that we have here, except over there, it was like-- it was like a pub.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You went in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You could have a sandwich.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they used to make you spritzers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A big thing was a spritzer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We used to have sweet wine with club soda together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that's what we used to have.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they used to sell herrings at the same time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I used to love-- my father used to take me in for spritzers and herrings and some bread.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I have some nice remembrances.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Your father took you in--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the pubs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the pubs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was before the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
